content: User is evaluating franchise opportunities with Seth. They plan to run a business together with their wife, who has a background in computer/networking support and is a real estate agent passionate about real estate investing. They have successfully worked together on a real estate investment property. Their shared interests have led them to consider specific business areas. They also have a dog with allergies, leading to an interest in pet-related ventures, and they enjoy visiting markets together on weekends. They aim for a business that aligns with these interests and are seeking a net income of $150K per year.
